text: Farhana Nariswari Wisandana (Sundanese script: ᮖᮁᮠᮔ ᮔᮛᮤᮞ᮪ᮝᮛᮤ ᮝᮤᮞᮔ᮪ᮓᮔ; born 28 May 1996) is an Indonesian model, doctor, advocate, and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Puteri Indonesia 2023. She will represent Indonesia at the Miss International 2023 pageant which will be held in Tokyo, Japan. == References == Category:Living people Category:Indonesian actors Category:Indonesian activists Category:1996 births
title: Farhana Nariswari
